  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      This open-label, multicenter trial will evaluate the efficacy and safety of treatment with
      AMN107 in chronic myelogenous leukemia (CML) patients that are resistant and/or intolerant to
      imatinib mesylate therapy.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
